methods.andEqual:

 set to false if the corresponding values are not equal.

:param destination: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableBooleanChunk) - the chunk to write equality values into

For each pair of indices i and i + 1 in chunk; if destination[i] is false do nothing, otherwise write true to
 destination[i] if they are equal.

 valuesChunk[chunkPositionsToCheckForEquality[pp * 2 + 1]] for each even/odd pair in
 chunkPositionsToCheckForEquality and writes the result to destinations.

:param destinations: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableBooleanChunk) - the destination chunk to write equality values into
